body: "GH-604. pm history <id> --verify prints verification.ok:false on a forked/broken chain but still exits 0, and there is no --strict-exit (validate has --strict-exit/--fail-on-warn). CI/merge hooks cannot gate on the obvious command. Fix: add --strict-exit via the full new-flag checklist; document default vs strict behavior."
